snippet.title: Evergate - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Evergate is a passion project for us, a game made with all our hearts. We are in love with its story, world, and characters, and we can't wait to share it all with you. But we need your help to get there!

Please give our Kickstarter trailer a watch and then head over to our project page to help us make Evergate a reality!

https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/stonelanterngames/evergate/
